metadata.name: Tentōmushi
metadata.description:
It is said that the 7 spots on the backs of ladybugs represent 7 different sorrows in the world. So, "Tentōmushi" is not lucky, contrary to popular belief.It takes all the bad luck herself so everyone else can live in serenity. I don't need luck. I create my own luck and I believe in it.That's why people always say you're lucky.This is the destiny of "Tentōmushi".I take all the bad luck to make my own luck

Tiger as spirit animal; independence, self-confidence, strength to overcome obstacles

4000 x 4000px

2023
